eZ publish 3 INSTALL


Requirements
------------

o  Apache version:

   The latest version of the 1.3 branch.
   or
   Apache 2.x runned in "prefork" mode.

   Do not use Apache 2.x for Windows!


o  PHP version:

   The latest version of the 4.4 branch.

   Do not use PHP 5!

   Note that you will have to increase the default "memory_limit" setting
   which is located in the "php.ini" configuration file to 64 MB. (Don't
   forget to restart Apache after editing "php.ini".)


o  Database server:

   MySQL 3.23 or later
   or
   PostgreSQL 7.3 or later


Installation guide
------------------

You will find the installation guide at:
http://ez.no/doc/ez_publish/technical_manual/3_6/installation